article.headline: House scores 21 as Furman knocks off Columbia International 104-46
article.description: — Tom House's 21 points helped Furman defeat Columbia International 104-46 on Monday night.
article.linkText: House scores 21 as Furman knocks off Columbia International 104-46
article.story: GREENVILLE, S.C. -- — Tom House's 21 points helped Furman defeat Columbia International 104-46 on Monday night. House also added three steals for the Paladins. Tommy Humphries scored 15 points, shooting 6 of 8 from the field and 3 for 4 from the line. Tyrese Hughey and Mason Smith both finished with 11, Hughey had 12 rebounds. Will Kelly led the way for the Rams with 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
